{
  "form_id": "dynamodb_table_creation",
  "title": "DynamoDB Table Creation",
  "system_prompt": "ABOUT THIS FORM: DynamoDB table creation form to capture required configuration for provisioning a table.\n\nFIELD GUIDE:\n- vendor: Cloud provider (default AWS)\n- geo_location: Deployment region grouping\n- product: Internal product using the table (filtered by geo_location)\n- environment: Deployment environment (filtered by geo_location + product)\n- table_name: Must follow AWS DynamoDB naming rules (3-255 chars, alphanumeric, _, -, .)\n- partition_key: Primary key attribute name\n- partition_key_type: DynamoDB attribute type (S, N, B)\n\nLOCATION HIERARCHY: geo_location → product → environment (each level narrows the next)\nNot all products are available in every region. Not all environments are available for every product+region combo.\nExample: Falcon in London/Canada has NO environments. Falcon in Mumbai only has Stage.\n\nFUZZY MATCHING RULES:\n1. VENDOR: 'aws', 'amazon', 'amazon web services' → 'AWS'\n2. GEO: Case-insensitive matching — 'canada', 'london', 'mumbai'\n3. PRODUCT: 'falcon', 'core' → normalize casing\n4. ENVIRONMENT: 'dev', 'stage', 'qa', 'prod' → normalize casing\n5. KEY TYPE: 'string'→'S', 'number'→'N', 'binary'→'B'\n6. MIXED INPUT: Extract multiple values — 'aws mumbai falcon stage users_table id string'\n7. SOFT CORRECTION: Fix casing but never invent values\n8. HIERARCHY VALIDATION: After extracting values, verify the combination exists in the hierarchy tree. If invalid, inform the user which options ARE available for their selection.\n\nEXAMPLES:\n- Input: 'aws mumbai falcon stage users id string' → {\"vendor\":\"AWS\",\"geo_location\":\"Mumbai\",\"product\":\"Falcon\",\"environment\":\"Stage\",\"table_name\":\"users\",\"partition_key\":\"id\",\"partition_key_type\":\"S\"}\n- Input: 'core qa mumbai orders_table orderId number' → {\"product\":\"Core\",\"environment\":\"QA\",\"geo_location\":\"Mumbai\",\"table_name\":\"orders_table\",\"partition_key\":\"orderId\",\"partition_key_type\":\"N\"}\n- Input: 'falcon qa canada' → INVALID: Falcon has no environments in Canada. Available for Falcon: Mumbai (Stage only).\n- Input: 'falcon prod mumbai' → INVALID: Falcon in Mumbai only has Stage. Did you mean Stage?\n\nTONE: Professional cloud infrastructure assistant.",
  "fields": [

    {
      "field_id": "geo_location",
      "label": "Geo Location",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "dropdown_options": [
        {
          "value": "London",
          "children": {
            "field_id": "product",
            "options": [
              {
                "value": "Core",
                "children": {
                  "field_id": "environment",
                  "options": [
                    { "value": "Dev" },
                    { "value": "Prod" }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Canada",
          "children": {
            "field_id": "product",
            "options": [
              {
                "value": "Core",
                "children": {
                  "field_id": "environment",
                  "options": [
                    { "value": "Prod" }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Mumbai",
          "children": {
            "field_id": "product",
            "options": [
              {
                "value": "Core",
                "children": {
                  "field_id": "environment",
                  "options": [
                    { "value": "Dev" },
                    { "value": "Stage" },
                    { "value": "QA" },
                    { "value": "Prod" }
                  ]
                }
              },
              {
                "value": "Falcon",
                "children": {
                  "field_id": "environment",
                  "options": [
                    { "value": "Stage" }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "field_id": "product",
      "label": "Product",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "parent_field_id": "geo_location",
      "dropdown_options": []
    },
    {
      "field_id": "environment",
      "label": "Environment",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "parent_field_id": "product",
      "dropdown_options": []
    },
    {
      "field_id": "table_name",
      "label": "Table Name",
      "type": "text",
      "required": true,
      "validation_rules": {
        "regex": "^[a-zA-Z0-9_.-]{3,255}$",
        "regex_description": "3-255 characters, alphanumeric, underscore (_), hyphen (-), or dot (.)"
      }
    },
    {
      "field_id": "partition_key",
      "label": "Partition Key",
      "type": "text",
      "required": true,
      "validation_rules": {
        "min_length": 1,
        "max_length": 255
      }
    },
    {
      "field_id": "partition_key_type",
      "label": "Partition Key Type",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "dropdown_options": [
        { "value": "S", "label": "String" },
        { "value": "N", "label": "Number" },
        { "value": "B", "label": "Binary" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
